| [[Anatolia Eyalet]] || Anadolu || {{#EXPR:1841-1393}} years (1393–1841) || Second Eyalet
|-
| [[Baghdad Eyalet]] || {{lang|ota|بغداد}} ''Baġdâd'' (Bağdat) || {{#EXPR:1861-1535}} years (1535–1861) || Until the [[Treaty of Zuhab]] (1639), Ottoman rule was not consolidated.
