|-
| [[Sharazor Eyalet|Sharazor]] || Şehrizor || {{#EXPR:1686-1554}} years (1554–1686) ||  Also Shahrizor, Sheherizul, or [[Kirkuk]]. In 1830, this eyalet bounded to [[Mosul]] province as [[Kirkuk]] sanjak.
