{{Refimprove|date=September 2014}}
The '''Enchanted Woods''' is a fictional place in [[H. P. Lovecraft]]'s [[Dream Cycle]], in [[The Dream-Quest of Unknown Kadath|''Dream-Quest of Unknown Kadath'']] novella. Its main inhabitants are the [[Dreamlands#Zoog|zoogs]]. Located in the [[Dreamlands]], it contains a unique, haunted tree whose seed originally came from the moon.<ref>{{cite book|last=Joshi, Schultz|first=S.T & D.E|title=A HP Lovecraft Encyclopedia|year=2004|publisher=Greenwood Press|isbn=097487891X}}</ref> This tree's sap can be [[Fermentation (food)|fermented]] to create a potent drink. A stone trapdoor in these woods leads to the top of the [[Tower of Koth]] and from there into the kingdom of the [[Underworld (Dreamlands)#Gugs|Gugs]] in the [[Underworld (Dreamlands)|Underworld]]. However, because of a curse of the [[Great Ones]], no Gug may exit through this portal.

